->snap): {overhang3}")\n\n# Overhang 4: snap to vector (position 1554)\noverhang4 = output[1554:1558].upper()  # TGAG\nprint(f"Overhang 4 (snap->vector): {overhang4}")\n\nprint("\\n" + "="*60)\nprint("PRIMER DESIGN")\nprint("="*60)\n\n# For BsaI-HFv2:\n# Recognition: GGTCTC\n# Cuts after: GGTCTC(N)1/5 - leaves 4bp overhang\n# Forward primer: GGTCTC N [4bp overhang] [template binding]\n# Reverse primer: GAGACC N [4bp overhang RC] [template binding RC]\n\nprint("\\nBsaI site: GGTCTC (cuts 1bp downstream on top, 5bp on bottom)")\nprint("This creates a 4bp overhang")\n\nEOF\npython3 design_gg_primers.py\n'] min_timeout_sec: 1 max_timeout_sec: 180.0
